{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d175529bc4","title":"对列宁反对第二国际机会主义斗争的一批材料的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d32f70fae1","index":0,"year":1962,"month":12,"day":22,"articleId":"d175529bc4"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji45","name":"毛泽东全集第45卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/45-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji45":{"comments":[{"id":"0d59bcc96d","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"d175529bc4","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中共中央宣传部1962年12月14日编印的《宣教动态》第一O九期刊登的列宁反对第二国际机会主义斗争的材料。材料的主要内容有：一恩格斯逝世到斯图加特大会：二、哥本哈根大会到巴塞尔大会；三、大战爆发到齐美尔瓦尔得代表会议；四、齐美尔瓦尔得代表会议；五、昆塔尔会议；六、齐美尔瓦尔得的破产与第三国际的建立。另有附件：一、巴塞尔大会宣言；二、关于大战爆发后第二国际政党的叛变的几个文件；三、俄国社会民主党的宣言；四、齐美尔瓦尔得左派的几个文件。"},{"id":"47491b876d","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"d175529bc4","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"柯老，指柯庆施，当时任中共中央政治局委员、中共上海市委第一书记。"},{"id":"de90a6b8d1","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"d175529bc4","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指参加中共中央政治局会议的同志。"},{"id":"461265befc","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"d175529bc4","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"李克用，唐朝沙陀部人，曾封为晋王。后其子李存助建立后唐，他被尊为太祖。"},{"id":"08bea109ba","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"d175529bc4","index":5,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"《三垂冈》这首诗为清朝诗人严遂成所作，毛泽东将它写在这一期《宣教动态》最后一页的空白处。"}],"contents":[{"id":"36daaf61d5","type":"title","text":"对列宁反对第二国际机会主义斗争的一批材料的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"d175529bc4"},{"id":"0d59bcc96d","type":"subtitle","text":"柯老”：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"d175529bc4"},{"id":"47491b876d","type":"paragraph","text":"此件很重要，请你印发会议各同志。大家读一、二遍，并讨论两天。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"d175529bc4"},{"id":"de90a6b8d1","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"d175529bc4"},{"id":"461265befc","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月二十二日古诗一首。咏后唐李克用和其儿子后唐庄宗李崇（存）勤诗。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"d175529bc4"},{"id":"08bea109ba","type":"subtitle","text":"三垂冈","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"d175529bc4"},{"id":"5ba27fdcab","type":"paragraph","text":"英雄立马起沙陀，","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"d175529bc4"},{"id":"745a9c93d9","type":"paragraph","text":"奈此朱梁践息何。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"d175529bc4"},{"id":"599c72a577","type":"paragraph","text":"只手难扶唐社程，","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"d175529bc4"},{"id":"43a61e5ed9","type":"paragraph","text":"连城犹（且）拥晋山河。","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"d175529bc4"},{"id":"505859cc0b","type":"paragraph","text":"风云帐下奇儿在，","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"d175529bc4"},{"id":"d31869a155","type":"paragraph","text":"鼓角灯前老泪多。","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"d175529bc4"},{"id":"e329746a6f","type":"paragraph","text":"萧（瑟）三垂冈下（畔）路，","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"d175529bc4"},{"id":"2aefa009de","type":"paragraph","text":"至今人唱百年歌。","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"d175529bc4"}],"page":{"id":"3d70d82be1","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"d175529bc4","start":302,"end":303}}}},"__N_SSG":true}